raw_meta_yaml:
context:
  version: 1.0.7
  python_min: "3.8"

package:
  name: httpcore
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/h/httpcore/httpcore-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8551cb62a169ec7162ac7be8d4817d561f60e08eaa485234898414bb5a8a0b4c

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: python
  script: python -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python ${{ python_min }}
    - hatchling
    - hatch-fancy-pypi-readme
  run:
    - python >=${{ python_min }}
    - h11 >=0.13,<0.15
    - h2 >=3,<5
    - sniffio 1.*
    - anyio >=3.0,<5.0
    - certifi

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - httpcore
      pip_check: true
  - requirements:
      run:
        - python ${{ python_min }}
    script:
      - python -c "import httpcore"

about:
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE.md
  summary: The next generation HTTP client.
  homepage: https://github.com/encode/httpcore

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - nicoddemus
    - synapticarbors
